main event: Unidentified personnel at Marshall Air Force Base, Kansas reported sighting a beam-shaped object over the base from 10:15 to 11:15 on May 25, 1953.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 1 hour.
The sighting was reported by unidentified personnel from the Operations Section at Marshall AFB.
The document is a Project Blue Book case file, indicating this was part of the official U.S. Air Force investigation into UFOs.
The document is marked as 'Unclassified' and includes declassification instructions.
witnesses: unidentified personnel from the Operations Section
